description.desc: Increases the crossbow mastery as well as weapon attack.  Only applied with a crossbow equipped.
description.name: Marksman Boost

description.desc: Increase party's all stats by certain percentage
description.name: 메이플 용사

description.desc: Fires a special arrow that penetrates through monsters. The arrow's power increases with each monster it pierces, inflicting more damage to each consecutive monster.
description.name: Piercing Arrow

description.desc: Grants party members the ability to locate enemy weaknesses, and in turn inflict more damage by exploiting them.
description.name: Sharp Eyes

description.desc: Drawing upon the spirit of the dragon, fires a powerful arrow of tremendous force that will knock back the target a long distance.
description.name: Dragon's Breath

description.desc: Temporarily summons the Frostprey, an ice-based hawk. Attacks up to 4 monsters.
description.name: Frostprey

description.desc: Delivers a blinding strike that impairs a monster's vision with a certain success rate, decreasing its accuracy.
description.name: Blind

description.desc: Delivers a lethal blow to a monster by aiming for its weak spot.
description.name: Snipe

description.desc: 용사의 의지특정 상태 이상에서 벗어날 수 있다. 레벨이 올라감에 따라 해제할 수 있는 상태 이상이 늘어난다.
description.name: 용사의 의지
